RESTAURAUNT-BILLING

THIS IS A JAVA PROJECT IMPLEMENTING BASIC CONCEPTS. 
SOFTWARE REQUIRED-ANY JAVA IDE[PROJECT WAS MADE USING BLUEJ]

OVERVIEW


This project is a basic restraunt billing system developed using the java.
The modules contained are : MENU , billing interface.
The interface is developed for the cashier where he/she select items from menu and generate a bill.

SOFTWARE
The code was developed using BLUEJ IDE and any similar developement environments can be used to run the project.

